### Register User
POST http://localhost:7001/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "passwordHash": "password123",
  "email": "testuser@example.com",
  "phone": "1234567890",
  "role": "CUSTOMER"
}

### Login User
POST http://localhost:7001/auth/login?username=testuser&password=password123
Content-Type: application/json

> {%
    client.global.set("auth_token", response.body.accessToken);
%}

### Apply for a Loan
POST http://localhost:8001/loans/apply
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "customerId": "CUST12345",
  "amount": 50000.00,
  "interestRate": 10.5,
  "tenureMonths": 24
}

### Get My Loans
GET http://localhost:8001/loans/my-loans?customerId=CUST12345
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Approve Loan (Replace {id} with actual Loan ID)
PUT http://localhost:8001/loans/1/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
